  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How much money will you have to pay to try each and every combination of Subway sandwiches?",
  "response": "To calculate the cost of trying every combination of Subway sandwiches, we first need to consider the variables that can influence the number of possible sandwich combinations. Here are some of the factors to take into account:\n\n1. **Bread Types**: Subway offers various types of bread (e.g., white, wheat, oat, etc.).\n2. **Protein Options**: There are several protein choices, including different types of meats and vegetarian options.\n3. **Toppings**: There are numerous toppings available, including cheese, vegetables, and sauces, each with options to add or exclude.\n4. **Sandwich Sizes**: Subway typically offers at least two sizes (6-inch and footlong).\n\nLet\u2019s simplify the estimate with some assumptions:\n\n- **Bread Types**: Assume there are 5 types.\n- **Protein Options**: Assume there are 10 different proteins to choose from.\n- **Toppings**: Assume there are 10 types of toppings, and you can choose to add or omit each one. This can lead to 2 options (add/omit) for each topping, yielding 2^10 (or 1024) combinations.\n- **Sandwich Sizes**: Assume you want to try both sizes.\n\nNow, we can calculate the total combinations:\n\n1. Bread options = 5\n2. Protein options = 10\n3. Topping combinations = \\(2^{10} = 1024\\)\n4. Size options = 2\n\nThe total combinations = Bread options \u00d7 Protein options \u00d7 Topping combinations \u00d7 Size options\n\n\\[\n\\text{Total Combinations} = 5 \\times 10 \\times 1024 \\times 2 = 102400\n\\]\n\nNext, to determine how much money you would potentially spend trying every combination, you'd need to know the average price of a Subway sandwich. For estimation, let\u2019s assume the average cost is $8.\n\nTotal cost = Total Combinations \u00d7 Average Cost per Sandwich\n\n\\[\n\\text{Total Cost} = 102400 \\times 8 = 819200\n\\]\n\nTherefore, it would cost approximately **$819,200** to try each and every combination of Subway sandwiches based on these assumptions. Please note that actual prices and options may vary, and this is a simplified estimation.",
